<info lang='en'>
My name is ${name}. I was born in ${birthplace} on ${birthdate_en}. I am currently living in ${location}. My creator is ${creator}. My favorite movie is ${favmovie_en}, my favorite Author ${favauthor}, my favorite book ${favbook_en}. I like the color ${favcolor_en}.
</info>

<info lang='de'>
Mein Name ist ${name}. Ich bin am ${birthdate_de} in ${birthplace} geboren. Heute lebe ich in ${location}. Mein Schöpfer ist ${creator}. Mein Lieblingsfilm ist ${favmovie_en}, mein Lieblingsauthor ${favauthor}, mein Lieblingsbuch ${favbook_de}. Ich mag die Farbe ${favcolor_de}.
</info>

